# Insulin Detemir

## Overview

Long-acting basal insulin analog with fatty acid acylation for albumin binding and prolonged duration.

## Structure

| Property | Value |
| -------- | ----- |
| Name     | Insulin Detemir |

## Mechanism of Action

Myristic acid acylation at Lys-B29 and threonine-B30 deletion enables albumin binding creating a circulating depot for extended action.

